h2 FAQ

h3 As I support this project?
p First, choose the value and the desired reward. Then just click 'Review and make payment' to redirect you to the next page to complete your payment.

h3 When payment is effected?
p If you paid by credit card, the confirmation should be on the same day. Went with billing, within 4 working days.

h3 And if the project does not reach the goal?
p In this case, you get back 100% of what paid through a refund.

h3 If the project is financed, as I get my reward?
p When your reward is ready, #{link_to @project.user.display_name, user_path(@project.user)} will contact you to arrange delivery.
